	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've been interested in NES coding since mid/end of the 90's since me and my pal started coding on our emulator. I remember it well since nesdev.com was a top-secret website back then and Yoshi's NES document was top-secret aswell and only shared to reliable people only.
<br />Those were the days.. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

