		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I started rom hacking around 2000 or so and was interested in rom expansion. Every document I looked at said something along the lines of "Nes rom expansion is impossible. If you don't know how, don't try, and those that do know why." Eventually I ended up at nesdev and homebrew kinda trumped rom hacking for me.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


